    "source": "# Bronze Layer: Media Playback Events\n\nThis notebook ingests raw streaming media playback events into the Bronze layer.\n\n## Data Source\n- **Type:** Parquet files from media event generator\n- **Location:** Files/output/bronze_media_events.parquet\n\n## Target\n- **Table:** bronze_media_events\n- **Format:** Delta Lake\n- **Mode:** Append\n\n## Compliance\n- COPPA: age_bucket field for downstream filtering\n- GDPR: pseudonymized user_id only (no PII)"
